青桐高中Etora正式加入，Moemi也加入，并成立自己的工作室https://p2y.jp/aogiri-high-school-etra-officially-joined-moemi-newly-joined-and-builted-own-studio/ https://p2y.jp/aogiri-high-school-etra-officially-joined-moemi-newly-joined-and-builted-own-studio/#respondp2y_admin Tue, 26 Mar 2024 15:00:00 +0000 VTuberバーチャルTwitterviviONYouTubeYouTuberあおぎり高校エトラバーチャルYouTuber株式会社ICT萌実 https://p2y.jp/?p=120067 <p> VTuber团体青雾高中（viviON株式会社运营）在2024年3月26日发布的视频中宣布，曾在团体中限时活跃的Etra正式加入团体。新[…]</p>后<a href="https://p2y.jp/aogiri-high-school-etra-officially-joined-moemi-newly-joined-and-established-own-studio/">青桐高中Etora正式加入，Moemi也加入，新成立的公司工作室</a>首次出现在<a href="https://p2y.jp">P2y.jp</a>上。; <p></p><p> VTuber团体<strong>青桐高中</strong>（viviON株式会社运营）在2024年3月26日发布的视频中宣布，此前限时活跃在团体中的<strong>Etora</strong>正式加入团体。宣布<strong>Moemi</strong>将加入该组合。 </p><p></p><figure class="wp-block-image size-full"><img fetchpriority="high" decoding="async" width="1200" height="675" data-attachment-id="120089" data-permalink="https://p2y.jp/aogiri-high-school-etra-officially-joined-moemi-newly-joined-and-established-own-studio/aogiri_high_school_etra_officially_joined_moemi_newly_joined_and_established_own_studio/" data-orig-file="https://p2y.jp/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/aogiri_high_school_etra_officially_joined_moemi_newly_joined_and_established_own_studio.jpg" data-orig-size="1200,675" data-comments-opened="1" data-image-meta="{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}" data-image-title="aogiri_high_school_etra_officially_joined_moemi_newly_joined_and_established_own_studio" data-image-description="" data-image-caption="" data-medium-file="https://p2y.jp/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/aogiri_high_school_etra_officially_joined_moemi_newly_joined_and_established_own_studio.jpg" data-large-file="https://p2y.jp/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/aogiri_high_school_etra_officially_joined_moemi_newly_joined_and_established_own_studio.jpg" src="https://p2y.jp/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/aogiri_high_school_etra_officially_joined_moemi_newly_joined_and_established_own_studio.jpg" alt="" class="wp-image-120089"/><figcaption class="wp-element-caption">图片来源：YouTube<br> © 2023 青桐高中 / viviON, inc.</figcaption></figure><p> Moemi是隶属于ICT Co., Ltd.的人才，Etora在加入集团之前就属于ICT Co., Ltd.。他是早期的资深人才之一，于 2017 年 3 月 3 日（平成 29 年）以“2D YouTuber”出道，当时 VTuber 这个词还不存在，最近他决定加入青桐高中。 。 </p><p></p><figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-video is-provider-youtube wp-block-embed-youtube wp-embed-aspect-16-9 wp-has-aspect-ratio"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper"><div class="youtube"><iframe title="【重要通知】我不会说再见..." src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/w9MypK6fIns?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></div></div></figure><p></p><figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-rich is-provider-twitter wp-block-embed-twitter"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper"><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="550" data-dnt="true"><p lang="ja" dir="ltr">这次，我将和萌美一起正式加入青桐高中！<br>我真的很感激在经过一年的临时调动后能够继续以这个身份工作。<br>谢谢，继续。<br><br>今天我们还有一些其他的公告，所以我们希望能够在晚上 9:30 左右播出！ <a href="https://t.co/g5KU1gYT3h">https://t.co/g5KU1gYT3h</a></p> — Etra/étra (@etra_ASI) <a href="https://twitter.com/etra_ASI/status/1772569043037192238?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">2024 年 3 月 26 日</a></blockquote><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></div></figure><p></p><figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-video is-provider-youtube wp-block-embed-youtube wp-embed-aspect-16-9 wp-has-aspect-ratio"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper"><div class="youtube"><iframe title="【通知】青桐高中正式加入？今天这还不是全部！ ！ ！ 【#江藤直播】" src="htt